article_title: UnitedHealth Sees 2016 Revenue Slightly Below Estimates
article_text:
UnitedHealth Group Inc., ahead of its investor day on Tuesday, projected revenue next year that falls just shy of analysts’ estimates, less than two weeks after it said weak performances on public health exchanges would cut into profit.

UnitedHealth said it expects 2016 revenue of $180 billion to $181 billion, while analysts polled by Thomson...
